A '''Cart00ney''' or '''Cartooney''' (usually spelled with the two zeroes) is a fictitious attorney or other lawyer invoked as a threat, or such a threat of legal action.  The word is a [[neologism]] originally coined in the [[Usenet]] [[newsgroup]] [[news.admin.net-abuse.email]] to describe the lawyers that [[spammer]]s threaten to let loose on those who identify them or block them &mdash; for example, being added to [[blacklist]]s &mdash; as well as the threats themselves.


